name: Aries hidden in stained glass
description:
Stained glass has always been a sign of happiness as it brings colorful light to dark places. Here it’s hiding not only a sign but it’s associated objects. 
 
ARIES TRAITS:
No filter 
Gets angry, then forgets why they were angry 
Thinks everything is a game they can win 
Will do anything on a dare 
Easily bored
